OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1781021474
OL,3,CThousands of doctors to walk out in
OL,4,Ctwo-day strike over pay
OL,6,FThousands of hospital doctors across
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland are set to walk out
OL,8,Flater this month in a major escalation
OL,9,Fof a bitter pay dispute.
OL,11,FHealth Trusts are bracing for
OL,12,Fdisruption after both resident and
OL,13,Fconsultant doctors voted to strike for
OL,14,F24 hours on Thursday June 25 and
OL,15,FMonday June 29.
OL,17,FA third group of hospital doctors has
OL,18,Fthreatened to join the planned
OL,19,Findustrial action. The result of a
OL,20,Fballot by specialist medics is
OL,21,Fexpected on Friday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
