PN,44705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1781021474
OL,3,CThousands of doctors to walk out in
OL,4,Ctwo-day strike over pay
OL,6,FResident doctors plan to stage their
OL,7,F24 hour strike from 7am on Monday June
OL,8,F29.
OL,10,FEven though the strikes are on
OL,11,Fseparate days, there is the very real
OL,12,Fpotential for widespread cancellation
OL,13,Fof clinics, operations and elective
OL,14,Fcare.
OL,16,FThe announcement of strike action
OL,17,Fcomes at a particularly awkward moment
OL,18,Ffor Health Minister Mike Nesbitt and
OL,19,Fhis department.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
