PN,44706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1781021474
OL,3,CThousands of doctors to walk out in
OL,4,Ctwo-day strike over pay
OL,6,FIn recent weeks the Department of
OL,7,FHealth has been highlighting falling
OL,8,Fwaiting lists, more elective
OL,9,Fprocedures, progress on long waits and
OL,10,Fdelivery of elective care targets.
OL,12,FBut strike action could test that
OL,13,Fmomentum, with concerns that some of
OL,14,Fthe gains could be disrupted.
OL,16,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,17,FITVX
